snippet.title: Evercade - THEC64 Collection 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
Home computer is back on Evercade. THEC64 Collection 2 brings 14 more games from the classic computer system to Evercade devices. Play with a friend on Evercade VS or play on the go, taking home computer games with you on Evercade Handheld or EXP.

Available April 2023
Pre-order from February 17th 2023

Find out more here: https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/thec64-collection-2/

Full Games List:
California Games
Cybernoid
Firelord
Impossible Mission II
Insects in Space
Mission Impossibubble
Nebulus
Pitstop II
Slayer
Street Sports Basketball
Sword of Fargoal
Uridum
World Games
Zamzara
